Audio Editor & Music Maker is an easy to operate music trimming and mixing  tool that allows you to easily cut and create music and make ringtones for iphone. It is a professional audio and music editor. Whethever you are a professional musician or music amateur, you can play easily.

Features:

1.Ringtones maker: you can edit and make personalized ringtones at will;
2.Audio extractor: supporting video to audio, you can extract audio from youtube;
3.Audio editor: supporting music clips, mergers, mixing and other advanced features, and export your music files in mp3, wav, m4a, m4r and other formats;
4.Music merging: song editing and splicing as a whole,connect the favorite songs;
5.Music mixing: free to cut the two songs, mixed together to play, feel different music effects!
6.Recorder and voice changer: recorded audios can be edited directly, and added voice effects
7.Support Wi-Fi import music

